{"type": "article", "id": 24565, "title": "去葡萄牙度假，不要错过这个只有9间房的清新旅舍", "description": "无论外观还是设置都令人神清气爽。", "date": "2016-03-28T19:00:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3253, "name": "葡萄牙"}, {"id": 25485, "name": "旅舍"}, {"id": 25486, "name": "PAr"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 226, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121123sITvVpa3xuFrefmO.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>葡萄牙的建筑师 Vânia Brito Fernandes 有一套祖父的空房子，建于 1940 年代，已经荒废很久了。房子的位置很好，在葡萄牙最南边的海岸线 Algarve（阿尔加维），是一个盛产葡萄酒的度假地，当地有非常多风格各异的旅馆。建筑师在改造这里时还是把它做成了旅舍，她联合了工作室 <a href=\"http://www.parplataformadearquitectura.pt/c-a-s-a--c-h-atilde-reg.html\">PAr </a>的另外两个创始人 Joana 和 Susana e Vânia 一起设计。</p>\n<p>这块地是一个小院，包括一高一矮两个房子。她们并没有在结构上做多大的改动，保留了外用的楼梯和露台，重新刷白了墙面。这种纯白色的小房子立刻让人联想到希腊海岸的白色房子，有了度假的休闲气氛。院子外用木篱笆和铁丝网格闲散地围着，这两幢建筑依然处于田园风景之中。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121111vK9m823utHgiRDfs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121112SlLPb7Hu2eT6Md1O.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">不远处的一个水塘变成了游泳池。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121112EhuKjr9SyaZHNgV1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>较矮的房子最明显的特征是 4 个外用的楼梯，平行排列着像 4 个坡道，通向楼上的露台。楼梯下面打开了一个圆拱形通道，让这处建筑拥有简洁的几何感，这种略显累赘的做法也营造了一种轻松闲散的气氛。</p>\n<p class=\"\">这里的一楼有公共的火炉和餐厅，靠近楼梯处是 4 个并排的带浴室的房间。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121113aKkRcNHMPp1wJrIZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121113WZuqoxJAykIGlU4X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121114JCb4V0sPj5DI2d9l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121115rIkmTwJBKH0XciL7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>较高房子有两层楼，侧面是公用的弧形楼梯，楼下有客厅、厨房等公用空间和一个小的客房。二楼是 4 个并排的客房，它们的窗户正对着环礁湖。</p>\n<p class=\"\">室内的布置也保留了简单干净的整体气氛，墙面刷成了白色，没有任何多余的装饰，只在房间里面放上了一些必要家具，比如实木桌和沙发，是工作室自己做的，非常居家。门和窗基本上也是方形的缺口，不再做复杂的装裱。在一些细节处能看到当地的痕迹，比如地面上铺的红色的陶砖和从前遗留下的圆拱屋顶，保持一种原始质朴的气氛。</p>\n<p class=\"\">这个公用楼梯就非常耐看，它的外面是一个小的走廊，纯白色。当光线从不同角度照射时，每一个侧面的光影都不一样，显得静谧而柔和。坡形楼梯和走廊的屋面构成一个三角形的空缺，用几根细的白色铁圈连接，站在正面看似乎能感受到流动的光影。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121115aG2vfe7R5NztACY0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121116pnDbPzOCYxWHv0i1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121116wj2zpA3b95XJT8Fr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031211178XOxnwrzalEmcDJs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121117ULiCdy6ZWXcqAJh3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121117Zlx9420n6EqdNz3H.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">卧室也是白色的，在地面、桌面和床头灯等地方用了陶砖、木材和黄铜，它们的颜色相近，都有点缀的效果。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>浴室在白色的滑动门后面，地面有一个像水池的凹槽，作为浴缸使用。水龙头和花洒都使用了黄铜，在白色墙面和红色陶砖下是非常古典的点缀。</p>\n<p class=\"\">这家旅馆现在已经营业，这里是它的网站<a href=\"http://www.casamodesta.pt/en/house/\">casa</a>，去葡萄牙度假的话不妨一试。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121118Bx2cTsfbIHMFuEXg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121118YtPKSb8lVWn47J5p.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121119CPdWkrIoK7HeFZi0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121119kPScIEbv3HwFBlOt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121120sMtvD3HLgYIGmPB4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121120LhnjE0m4TtDoIukr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75232775\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121120g0UoLlVuJjTI5B2H.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.20619658\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121121bgnFqm083RuDCUNw.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.19017094\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121121aITAFki4H2rhpPuW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.20619658\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121122B1y4fjRPlLmKGTqo.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">一楼</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121122ybKdqPSxDUweLXtB.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">二楼</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121123dmDsTcbnAZaw5S9l.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78205128\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">屋顶</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/03/28/casa-modesta-par-algarve-portugal-hotel-renovation-external-staircases/\">dezeen</a>、<a href=\"http://www.casamodesta.pt/en/house/\">casa</a></p>\n\n\n"}